  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Mix the cooked brown rice with the candied ginger, black sesame seeds, turmeric, and a pinch of salt in a bowl.",
    "Arrange the uni pieces on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Drizzle the coconut oil over the uni and sprinkle with soy sauce, lime juice, garlic, and green chilies.",
    "Roast the uni in the preheated oven for 8-10 minutes or until slightly charred.",
    "Meanwhile, shape the rice mixture into small patties or squares.",
    "Once the uni is done, remove it from the oven and let it cool slightly.",
    "Add a piece of charred uni to each rice patty and serve immediately."
  ],
